cdata.name: Zoin
cdata.desc:
Zoin is a payment platform that uses the Zerocoin protocol. Users are able to transact ZOI tokens within the Zoin network. The Zerocoin protocol uses zero-knowledge proofs to ensure that financial transactions are anonymous.

The ZOI token uses the Lyra2RE algorithm and has the vision to create a coin that is evolving through the community, therefore the founder reward was removed.
